	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The thing about Retrozone products is you don't expect them to come out in a certain small span of time. Just one day it's there. No warning. <br /><br />All the flash carts are likely to play the main mappers fine. It's obscure mappers and special features that make them better or worse. One thing that is cool that I don't know if the N8 supports, is the realtime save states. There are realtime save state mappers for PowerPAK.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


